               <h2><a href="/hotoffpress" title=""></a></h2> 
               <h1 style="text-align: left;">Hot off the Press...&nbsp;&nbsp;</h1> 
               <h2 style="text-align: center;">Federal government invests $4.9 million in CO2 field research station</h2> 
               <p>University will be a partner in developing monitoring technologies at Canadaâ€™s first research site to understand underground storage. <a href="http://www.ucalgary.ca/utoday/issue/2015-02-17/federal-government-invests-49-million-co2-field-research-station?utm_source=UToday&amp;utm_medium=Email&amp;utm_campaign=February-17-2015&amp;utm_term=Federal%20government%20invests%20$4.9%20million%20in%20CO2%20field%20research%20station">Read more here.</a></p> 
               <hr width="100"> 
               <h2 style="text-align: center;">Six University of Calgary researchers awarded funding</h2> 
               <p>Congratulations to&nbsp;Bernhard Mayer,&nbsp;professor, Isotope Geochemistry, Department of Geoscience.&nbsp;<em>NSERC Funding: $513,884</em>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ucalgary.ca/utoday/issue/2015-02-10/six-university-calgary-researchers-awarded-funding">Read more here.</a>&nbsp;</p> 
